This control allows you to select the [http://wiki.wontology.org/wiki/help.php?title=WmHelp:GlossaryAtoO#anchor_Node node] which will be the [http://wiki.wontology.org/wiki/help.php?title=WmHelp:GlossaryPtoZ#anchor_Subject subject] of this edge.  The "subject" is the node about which this edge "makes a statement".  For example, in an edge which encapsulates the fact that "the sky is blue", "sky" is the subject.
